product_name: EssenceLash Princess False Lash Effect Mascara
summary: SummaryHighlightsClean IngredientsCruelty FreeGive BackEssence Lash Princess False Lash Effect Mascara creates an irresistible false lash effect with length, curl, and dramatic volume.
details: DetailsFeaturesFeatures iconic conical-shaped fiber brushMascara provides length, volume, and a false lash effectCruelty-freeOphthalmologist testedFormulated WithoutMicroplastic particlesParabensAlcoholLactoseOilPerfumeItem 2289595How To UseUsing essence Lash PRINCESS false lash effect mascara, start at the base of the lash line and wiggle wand back and forth, adding as many coats as you like until desired length and volume is achieved. Remove mascara with essence Remove Like A Boss Waterproof Eye Make-up Remover.IngredientsAqua (Water), Cera Alba (Beeswax), Paraffin, Glyceryl Stearate, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Bran Wax, Butylene Glycol, Palmitic Acid, Acacia Senegal Gum, Polybutene, Copernicia Cerifera Cera (Copernicia Cerifera (Carnauba) Wax), Aminomethyl Propanol, Stearic Acid, Vp/Eicosene Copolymer, Tocopherol, Hydroxyethyl cellulose, Dimethicone, Polyester-4, Ethylhexylglycerin, Sodium Nitrate, Phenoxyethanol, Potassium Sorbate, Ci 77499 (Iron Oxides).
how_to_use: Using essence Lash PRINCESS false lash effect mascara, start at the base of the lash line and wiggle wand back and forth, adding as many coats as you like until desired length and volume is achieved. Remove mascara with essence Remove Like A Boss Waterproof Eye Make-up Remover.

reviews.headline: WORST MASCARA I TRIED SO FAR
reviews.comments: This is one of the worst mascaras I have ever bought before. It clumps my lashes and doesn't apply as smoothly as others. I compared it to my go to mascara (Clinique mascara) on my hand and it barely even applied to my hand. The Clinique on applied smoothly.

reviews.headline: This mascara is amazing
reviews.comments: I was a huge fan of Stila mascara but it just became too expensive. Most other mascaras I've tried were dried out and did not work until I bought this mascara. It's thick, it's black, love it and the price can't be beat!.

reviews.headline: This is my fourth tube of this mascara I absolutely love it.
reviews.comments: You cannot convince me that there is a better mascara on the market. I have tried the expensive mascara, I have tried the tubing mascara, all of the gimmicks. And I continue to go back to this mascara. It is the absolute best.

reviews.headline: Inexpensive
reviews.comments: Does the job for less money!

reviews.headline: Yes I would buy this product again and again
reviews.comments: Love love, love this mascara you don't even need primer with it. Make sure lashes look longer thicker and luscious. However, I will try the waterproof one next time and it's very reasonably priced remarkable for the price I rated and 11 on a scale of 0 to 10.

reviews.headline: Works Great!
reviews.comments: I think this mascara works better than some of my higher end ones!  It goes on well and lasts.  I haven't even used my others ones since buying this one!!

reviews.headline: BUY NOW
reviews.comments: This is the absolute best mascara I have ever used. And its at an affordable cost. so like teens like me can afford it and get great lashes!!!10/10 recommend

reviews.headline: Nice Mascara for the Price
reviews.comments: Nice but compared to higher priced mascaras I found that this is messing when applying.  I always get dots on my lid or under the eye and that is applying to top lashes only.  I also didn't notice when I bought it that there was no protection seal, which would make me not buy this again.

reviews.headline: Favorite mascara
reviews.comments: I love this mascara and buy it in multiples.  My only complaint is that our local Ulta never has enough cashiers and that equals long lines.  :(

reviews.headline: Lovely Formula!
reviews.comments: I have always loved this mascara and came back to it recently wondering why I ever stopped using it to try anything else! I love the formula it's so fresh and separates my lashes so beautifully! I have beautiful defined lashes thanks to your mascara! I bought the two pack but I prefer this one but the waterproof one is still great too! Thank you so much for your product! It's cruelty free and clean ingredients! Lovely mascara!

reviews.headline: The best mascara
reviews.comments: I have used this mascara for over 3 years now and I have never had a single complaint with it. It gives the best long lash effect. it's also very good if you have shorter lashes [as I do] to give them added length. definitely a repurchase!

reviews.headline: i love it!!
reviews.comments: this mascara is one of the best ones i've ever owned. it really lifts and darkens your lashes! 100% recomend!

reviews.headline: Disappointed

reviews.headline: good price, good for tweens, too much product on brush

reviews.headline: It's ok‚Ä¶
reviews.comments: I got this in a gift set snd I mean, this mascara is fine. It lengthens reallt well and adds good volume, but DOES NOT hold a curl like AT ALL. I know thats not what it's advertised for, but my lashes fell within 30 seconds of putting this on. I had high hopes because I LOVE the waterproof version of this, but it dissapointed.

faceoff_positive.comments: I love this mascara! Ever since I discovered it, it's the only one I use! It makes my eyelashes so long and every time I use it I get compliments and get asked what mascara do I use. Thanks to this product I don't even need to wear false lashes.
faceoff_positive.headline: The BEST mascara in the world

faceoff_negative.comments: I have short, wimpy East Asian lashes that stick straight down and have trouble holding a curl so I always have to curl them before applying mascara. After hearing how beloved this mascara is by almost everyone I hoped it would work miracles, but unfortunately it doesn't. As soon as I apply it, my lashes get weighed down and start to sink and lose their curl. Although the mascara does add volume and length, I find that it tends to clump up and make my lashes stick together. It also stays wet for quite a while and has a tendency to smudge and flake on me. In the end it basically netted out to just an average mascara for me. Granted my lashes are difficult to work with but I figured this review would be helpful for those with similar issues.
faceoff_negative.headline: Too wet/heavy for short, weak lashes
